@Raymond Smith
Hearing an elected head of state would be helpful gives me hope that the Commonwealth should think about making that a goal for all Commonwealth Countries.
Maybe when Prince Charles becomes King of the United Kingdom, he could spearhead that change

@Tina Billiot
Exactly.  If the US wants Canada, it will have to invade our country.

But if the US invades Canada, it will be facing Canadians and our Commonwealth friends.  There will be many to stop them.

@Jonathan Bishop
I fear many people around the world are becoming selfish now.

However, the majority of Canadians are known for their positivity.  We do more to help others than any other nation.<|im_end|>
